# Novelty Polytechnic Landing Page ‚Äî Build Prompt

## Overview
Build a modern, responsive, SEO-optimized single-page landing page for **Novelty Polytechnic, Kishi** using **Next.js 16 (App Router)**, **Tailwind CSS v4**, **TypeScript**, and **lucide-react** icons. The page must feel like a professionally designed tertiary institution website ‚Äî clean, authoritative, and welcoming.

