## Design & UX Principles

1. **Visual Hierarchy** ‚Äî CTAs and headings stand out via size, color, spacing.
2. **Consistent Spacing** ‚Äî All sections: `py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`. Inner containers: `max-w-7xl mx-auto`.
3. **Mobile-First** ‚Äî Design for mobile, enhance up via `sm:`, `md:`, `lg:`, `xl:`.
4. **60-30-10 Rule** ‚Äî 60% neutral/white, 30% green, 10% amber accent.
5. **Touch Targets** ‚Äî All interactive elements `min-h-[44px]` minimum.
6. **Accessibility** ‚Äî Sufficient contrast ratios, `aria-label` on icon-only buttons.
7. **Animations** ‚Äî Pure CSS transitions (no framer-motion). Hover lifts, shadow changes, underline effects.
8. **Border Radius** ‚Äî `rounded-xl` for small cards, `rounded-2xl` for feature cards, `rounded-full` for buttons.

