## SEO Requirements

### Metadata (in `layout.tsx`)
Export a `metadata` object with:
- `title` (with template `"%s | Novelty Polytechnic, Kishi"`)
- `description` ‚Äî 155-160 chars including institution name, location, departments, phone
- `keywords` array ‚Äî 10-12 terms including "Novelty Polytechnic", "polytechnic in Oyo State", department names, "admission into polytechnic 2026"
- `openGraph` ‚Äî type: website, locale: en_NG, 1200x630 image
- `twitter` ‚Äî summary_large_image card
- `robots` ‚Äî index, follow with googleBot settings
- `icons` ‚Äî favicon/logo.ico

### JSON-LD Structured Data
Inject `application/ld+json` in the `<head>` with:
- `EducationalOrganization` schema including `@id`, name, alternateName, description, url, logo, address (PostalAddress), email, telephone, slogan, and `department` array (one `Department` entry per department).

### Sitemap (`sitemap.ts`)
Dynamic entries for: `/`, `/#about`, `/#departments`, `/#admission`, `/#contact`. Each with `lastModified`, `changeFrequency`, `priority`.

### Robots (`robots.ts`)
Allow `/`, disallow `/api/` and `/_next/`. Point sitemap to `https://noveltypolytechnic.edu.ng/sitemap.xml`.

### Heading Hierarchy
- **One H1:** Hero heading "Novelty Polytechnic, Kishi"
- **H2:** Each section title
- **H3:** Department names in cards
- CTAs are `<a>` tags with descriptive text (no heading tags)

### NAP Consistency
Name, Address, Phone identical across:
- JSON-LD structured data
- TopBar (visible)
- Footer (visible)
- Hero aside card

